Demo fonts may be used for testing and experimenting purposes only. This includes client presentations. Any professional or consumer facing projects require the purchase of a standard license. If the font will be transmitted or used by a client, the client must purchase an appropriate license.

Use in student work is permitted. Use by a student in paid work is not permitted.

Posting experimental or personal work to social media is permitted with an attribution of the typeface, tagging @ohnotypeco, and a compliment.

Modifications to the font software or the design embodied therein is not permitted.